+## Result inspection
 
-## í·© Design
+`AegisResult` includes:
 
-Aegis is:
+- `output`
+- `final_answer`
+- `metrics`
+- `actions`
+- `trace`
+- `used_fallback`
+- `explanation`
+- `scope`
+- `scope_data`
 
-* thin
-* backend-driven
-* runtime-focused
-* production-oriented
+Helpers:
 
-It does NOT:
+- `to_dict()`
+- `debug_summary()`
+- `to_log_record()`
 
-* replace your model
-* require retraining
-* expose internal engine complexity
+## Configuration
 
----
+`AegisConfig` fields (backend-aligned):
 
-## License
+- `mode` (`light | balanced | aggressive`)
+- `max_interventions`
+- `allow_retries`
+- `allow_retrieval_expansion`
+- `allow_context_reduction`
+- `allow_prompt_shaping`
+- `fallback` (`safe | baseline | strict`)
+- `explain`
+- `emit_trace`
+- `policy`
+- `timeout_ms`
 
-MIT
